<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="health-n">health <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /helθ/    美 /helθ/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>健康；卫生：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>health insurance / care</strong>
健康保险/医疗保健</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>physical and mental health</strong>
身心健康</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Going to bed early and getting up early does good to your health.
早睡早起有益健康。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="be-in-good-poor-health">(be) in good / poor health</h3>
<p>1.<strong>身体好 / 差：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My grandpa is 78 and in poor health.
我爷爷78岁了，身体不太好。</p></div></div>